reviewText: This is such a wonderful CD to learn to paint.  There are so many people would enjoy getting this CD.  I talked to Gary on the phone and was so delightful to talk to.  Some day I hope to be able to paint like Gary.
Love this video.  Very helpful. Love the jenkins style of painting.
Great DVD.  I love all of his books and dvds.

Looks like I'll have to get the book. Needed a little more instruction.
DVD s are hard to reverse and review.

Aileen
I really like this DVD.  It gives a lot more detail than you can find on tv.  I did my first painting along with Gary and I think it looks good enough to sell!  I will order more DVD's!
